    </div>
    <div class="prose-guido space-y-5 text-base leading-8 text-zinc-700">
      <h2>Download</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-1">
        <li><a href="http://guidochiesa.net/media/pressreview/materiale-resistente/1995/MATERIALE RESISTENTE 2.jpg" target="_blank" class="text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-800 transition">MATERIALE RESISTENTE 2.jpg</a></li>
